3a4f8170-1256-4abd-bae4-a2019076b0f2.2b1c133e-45f6-4c3b-8f1f-df279667aad1.description= 
Compares a files last modified date/time to a given threshold.

Input Parameters\:
source - the file to read
Threshold - the threshold to compare the file modified time to.
username - username to use when reading.
password - password to use when reading.

Responses\:
failure			- the operation failed. The file probably could not be found.
greater than	- The file's modified time is larger than the threshold.
less than		- The file's modified time is smaller than the threshold.
equal to		- The file's modified time is the same as the threshold.

Extra Results\:
date			- The file's modified time.
3a4f8170-1256-4abd-bae4-a2019076b0f2.31ab01b8-0111-4fe8-9c63-293768474338.description= 
Checks to see if a path points to a directory.

Input Parameters\:
source - the path to check
username - username to use when reading.
password - password to use when reading.

Responses\:
failure			- the operation failed. The path does not point to a directory.
success			- The operation succeeded.

Gets a list of files and folders in a directory.

Input Parameters\:
source - the directory to check
delimiter - A delimiter to put between files and folders in the directory.
username - username to use when reading.
password - password to use when reading.

returns\:
The children of the path.

Extra Results\:
count - the number of children.

Responses\:
failure			- the operation failed. The path probably could not be found, or was a file.
success			- The operation succeeded.

3a4f8170-1256-4abd-bae4-a2019076b0f2.description=
moves or removes windows log files from a folder.

Inputs\:
alternateStore - Where to put log files. They are deleted if null.
folder - Folder to clean of windows log files.
user - user to authenticate as.
password - password for user.
Old Threshold - Files before this date will be cleaned.

Responses\:
success - operation completed.
failure - something went wrong.
flow.name: Clean Logs
